snippet.textDisplay:
Benaam si khwaishein aawaz na mile Bandishein kyun khwaab pe?

parwaaz na mile. Jaane hai par, maane dil na, tu na mere liye. Bebasi yeh pukaar rahi hai, aa saajan mere. Benaam si khwaishein, aawaz na mile Chaand teri roshni, aftaab se hai magar Chaah ke bhi na mile hai, dono ki nazar Duriyaan, din raat ki hein, tai na ho fasle Benaam si khwaishein, aawaz na mile Patjhad jaaye, barkha aaye, ho bahar Mausam badalte rahe Dil ke nagar jo, basi sard hawaein Kyun na jaayein… Aa ja, aa bhi ja, mausam katte na, birah ke… Benaam si khwaishein, aawaz na mile
